description.en: GSMcoin is created to provide a service for users to unlock mobile devices that are locked to a certain network operator. By unlocking you mobile phone, you may swithc to a different operator with possibly lower costs. Users pay for the unlock service using GSMcoins. There is a 0.8% premine.
